WEBVTT

00:00:58.720 --> 00:01:04.176
and yet we exclude people who fit
our economic and demographic needs

00:01:04.200 --> 00:01:06.040
from coming to Europe.

00:01:07.000 --> 00:01:12.936
We proclaim our liberal values
in opposition to fundamentalist Islam,

00:01:12.960 --> 00:01:14.160
and yet --

00:01:15.560 --> 00:01:18.216
we have repressive policies

00:01:18.240 --> 00:01:20.560
that detain child asylum seekers,

00:01:21.160 --> 00:01:23.960
that separate children
from their families,

00:01:24.800 --> 00:01:27.720
and that seize property from refugees.

00:01:28.960 --> 00:01:30.200
What are we doing?